Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.88,0:00:42.96,Main,,0,0,0,,- Mister Shoichi?\N- His room.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.27,0:01:05.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Your mother's hospital's on fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.74,0:01:14.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.16,0:01:20.21,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll go too!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.33,0:01:22.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Stay here, Mahito!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.66,0:01:59.79,Main,,0,0,0,,<i>Mother...</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.68,0:02:22.27,Main,,0,0,0,,<i>Three years into the war,\NMother died.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.19,0:02:26.77,Main,,0,0,0,,<i>Four years in,\NI left Tokyo with Father.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.04,0:02:46.08,Main,,0,0,0,,<i>"Saginuma Station"</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.74,0:03:17.70,Main,,0,0,0,,That's her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.59,0:03:32.13,Main,,0,0,0,,<i>She looked exactly like Mother.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.38,0:03:34.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Did you wait long?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.09,0:03:36.59,Main,,0,0,0,,We just arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.09,0:03:40.10,Main,,0,0,0,,You're Mahito?\NI'm Natsuko.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.80,0:03:44.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Sorry I'm late.\NWe had a flat tire on the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.15,0:03:49.90,Main,,0,0,0,,You've grown up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.02,0:03:53.73,Main,,0,0,0,,I've met you once,\Nwhen you were a baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.23,0:03:55.65,Main,,0,0,0,,The factory first?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.86,0:03:57.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes. I'll be back for dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.12,0:04:05.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Perfect timing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.45,0:04:06.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Come, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.00,0:04:08.12,Main,,0,0,0,,That's heavy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.59,0:04:12.75,Main,,0,0,0,,After you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.97,0:04:26.06,Main,,0,0,0,,To the residence.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.61,0:04:40.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Mahito, I'm going to be your\Nnew mother. Did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.70,0:04:43.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Your hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.66,0:04:48.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Go on, put it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.92,0:04:52.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Feel it moving?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.21,0:04:58.63,Main,,0,0,0,,A baby. Your little\Nbrother or sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.80,0:05:00.55,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm so delighted.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.76,0:05:02.89,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, stop here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.01,0:05:06.22,Main,,0,0,0,,<i>"May your luck last long in battle"\N"Congratulations on your call-up"</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.02,0:05:58.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Alright, we're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.86,0:06:02.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Take the luggage in.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.58,0:06:13.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Mahito, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.30,0:06:23.34,Main,,0,0,0,,It's your first time,\Nso we'll enter from the front.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.93,0:06:32.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Look, over there.\NThat building.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.89,0:06:35.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Your father's new factory.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.27,0:06:38.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's visit it sometime.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.00,0:06:59.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh dear, no one's in.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.67,0:07:05.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Bring your shoes with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.33,0:07:37.08,Main,,0,0,0,,How rare. It's never\Nflown inside before.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.39,0:07:56.23,Main,,0,0,0,,That nosy gray heron.\NIt must be welcoming you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.01,0:08:29.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Well well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.14,0:08:32.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Opened Shoichi's trunk again?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.89,0:08:34.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, m'lady...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.85,0:08:37.48,Main,,0,0,0,,The pedicab man came,\Nya see!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.60,0:08:39.52,Main,,0,0,0,,He left it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.65,0:08:40.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Yup, yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.60,0:08:42.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Didn't know whose it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.40,0:08:43.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Yup, yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.90,0:08:45.57,Main,,0,0,0,,It smells so sweet...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.69,0:08:47.44,Main,,0,0,0,,So we just...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.61,0:08:52.03,Main,,0,0,0,,This is Shoichi's son, Mahito.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.95,0:09:37.91,Main,,0,0,0,,- What?!\N- Canned beef!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.25,0:09:40.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Tasty when cooked with rice!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.46,0:09:43.17,Main,,0,0,0,,Canned salmon!\NGimme the bones!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.63,0:09:46.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Corned beef!\NYou can still get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.80,0:09:48.38,Main,,0,0,0,,And lastly...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.51,0:09:50.51,Main,,0,0,0,,- Sugar!\N- Good for rice cakes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.63,0:09:51.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Sweet bean paste!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.88,0:09:55.26,Main,,0,0,0,,- Sweet rice cakes!\N- Pure white sugar!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.39,0:09:56.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Gimme a taste!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.97,0:09:58.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.43,0:10:00.52,Main,,0,0,0,,We can go now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.68,0:10:03.35,Main,,0,0,0,,So some places still have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.61,0:10:09.15,Main,,0,0,0,,He's his mother's spitting image.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.36,0:10:10.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Such a pretty boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.82,0:10:12.99,Main,,0,0,0,,I hope he stays safe...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.11,0:10:14.45,Main,,0,0,0,,You got smokes?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.57,0:10:16.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Gimme one!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.42,0:10:34.26,Main,,0,0,0,,This is your room.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.72,0:10:39.85,Main,,0,0,0,,You must be tired.\NI'll bring tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.13,0:12:35.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.76,0:12:39.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Mahito...\NGoodbye...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.47,0:12:43.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Mom! I'm coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.47,0:12:45.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Mahito...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.43,0:12:48.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Mahito...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.56,0:12:52.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.11,0:15:05.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Mahito!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.53,0:15:10.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Mahito!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.91,0:15:14.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Mahito!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.69,0:16:27.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Sonny!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.28,0:16:29.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Better head back!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.49,0:16:32.12,Main,,0,0,0,,The lady's worried about ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.16,0:16:35.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Sonny!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.33,0:16:42.63,Main,,0,0,0,,That used to be sealed off...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.84,0:16:46.46,Main,,0,0,0,,He'll get taken...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.17,0:16:48.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Sonny!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.80,0:16:50.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.89,0:16:52.01,Main,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.26,0:16:56.43,Main,,0,0,0,,There's a staircase.\NWhat's this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.93,0:16:59.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.19,0:17:01.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Better head back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.02,0:17:05.53,Main,,0,0,0,,The feathers are gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.99,0:17:14.49,Main,,0,0,0,,I was saving this story\Nfor when you get settled in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.74,0:17:20.50,Main,,0,0,0,,That tower was built by\Nmy mother's uncle, I was told.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.25,0:17:24.96,Main,,0,0,0,,He was a very smart man,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.71,0:17:28.88,Main,,0,0,0,,but read too many books,\Nand lost his mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.59,0:17:33.72,Main,,0,0,0,,<i>One day, a long time\Nbefore I was born,</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.68,0:17:39.39,Main,,0,0,0,,<i>he disappeared, leaving only\Nan open book he hadn't finished.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.31,0:17:44.36,Main,,0,0,0,,<i>They looked everywhere,\Nbut couldn't find any trace.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.94,0:17:50.90,Main,,0,0,0,,<i>Later, in a flood, a passage\Nto the main house collapsed,</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.45,0:17:54.95,Main,,0,0,0,,<i>and beneath the tower,\Na maze of tunnels was found.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.49,0:18:01.08,Main,,0,0,0,,For safety, my grandfather\Nhad the entrance sealed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.04,0:18:05.04,Main,,0,0,0,,You mustn't go near it either.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.67,0:18:08.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes ma'am.\NThank you for the tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.92,0:18:12.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.34,0:18:16.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Good night. Mornings are cold,\Nso sleep warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.14,0:18:17.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.57,0:19:20.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Mahito, save me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.76,0:19:34.88,Main,,0,0,0,,You're home.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.22,0:19:36.22,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.05,0:20:14.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Navy boys are all flustered.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.92,0:20:17.88,Main,,0,0,0,,They boasted Saipan\Nwould hold for a year.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.26,0:20:21.93,Main,,0,0,0,,I pity those who died...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.10,0:20:24.43,Main,,0,0,0,,The factory's booming though.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.56,0:20:27.52,Main,,0,0,0,,We'll take the Datsun to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.98,0:20:33.52,Main,,0,0,0,,A transfer student arriving by car\Nwill shock everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.94,0:20:39.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.\NWe've spoken to the teachers.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.28,0:20:41.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Off you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.21,0:20:52.21,Main,,0,0,0,,<i>"Agricultural volunteers"</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.13,0:21:02.14,Main,,0,0,0,,<i>"Mahito Maki"</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.01,0:22:25.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Mahito, tell me the truth.\NWho did this to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.06,0:22:28.64,Main,,0,0,0,,I just took a tumble.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.27,0:22:35.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Rest assured. I'll avenge you,\Nso tell me the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.27,0:22:36.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Shoichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.73,0:22:39.15,Main,,0,0,0,,I won't let them get away with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.86,0:22:41.15,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll go to his school.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.79,0:22:53.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Mahito! Save me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.25,0:22:55.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Mahito!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.04,0:22:57.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Mahito!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.27,0:23:12.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.98,0:23:19.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh my!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.44,0:23:23.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Mahito!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.49,0:23:24.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Shut this!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.26,0:23:47.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Mom! Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.69,0:24:07.32,Main,,0,0,0,,M'lady, please get some rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.49,0:24:11.03,Main,,0,0,0,,We'll take turns\Nkeeping an eye on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.68,0:27:18.93,Main,,0,0,0,,What are you?!\NNot an ordinary gray heron!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.10,0:27:29.86,Main,,0,0,0,,It seems the long-awaited one\Nhas appeared at last.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.27,0:27:33.53,Main,,0,0,0,,I shall now guide you to your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.03,0:27:37.66,Main,,0,0,0,,My mother?! How dare you!\NMy mother died!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.95,0:27:45.96,Main,,0,0,0,,A typical human trick.\NShe ain't dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.04,0:27:52.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Pardon me, but you did not\Nsee your mother's dead body.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.01,0:27:59.72,Main,,0,0,0,,She is awaiting your rescue.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.05,0:28:01.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Please join us...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.47,0:28:04.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Please join us...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.73,0:28:07.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Join us...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.40,0:28:09.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Join us...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.74,0:28:17.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Mahito!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.70,0:28:21.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Mahito!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.04,0:28:25.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Mahito!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.09,0:28:39.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Sonny!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.43,0:28:43.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Your presence is requested.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.02,0:29:38.03,Main,,0,0,0,,You're awake?\NThank heavens.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.11,0:29:47.37,Main,,0,0,0,,You were out for so long,\Nand we were so worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.33,0:29:49.54,Main,,0,0,0,,The gray heron...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.91,0:29:51.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Gray heron?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.33,0:29:54.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Is it near?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.17,0:29:56.71,Main,,0,0,0,,A dream, perhaps?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.84,0:29:59.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Mahito! You're awake.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.51,0:30:03.47,Main,,0,0,0,,Rest assured.\NI'll catch who did this to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.59,0:30:05.14,Main,,0,0,0,,I was just clumsy.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.26,0:30:07.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.\NNo school for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.02,0:30:11.31,Main,,0,0,0,,I donated 300 yen.\NThe principal was shocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.10,0:30:16.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Those teachers barely teach.\NToo much voluntary labor.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.69,0:30:20.86,Main,,0,0,0,,That might leave a bald spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.07,0:30:23.11,Main,,0,0,0,,It'll get covered up.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.37,0:30:29.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Natsuko isn't feeling well.\NShe's probably tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.87,0:30:31.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Try not to worry her.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.04,0:30:38.46,Main,,0,0,0,,The railway's stopped again.\NAlways accidents.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.59,0:30:40.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Get well soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.84,0:30:42.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Take care of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.31,0:30:58.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Sonny, take it easy and lie down.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.86,0:31:00.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.07,0:31:04.20,Main,,0,0,0,,But your bedpan's here...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.51,0:31:30.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, a lot's strange\Nabout this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.60,0:31:33.31,Main,,0,0,0,,In many ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.34,0:32:04.72,Main,,0,0,0,,You well enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.09,0:32:06.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.47,0:32:08.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Magnificent, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.80,0:32:12.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Can't leave them at the station,\Nso we came here.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.56,0:32:15.14,Main,,0,0,0,,They're beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.64,0:32:19.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Natsuko's worried about you.\NGo see her.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.98,0:32:20.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.57,0:32:26.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Men, well done!\NRest, then return to the factory!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.99,0:32:36.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Ain't to your liking, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.79,0:32:37.83,Main,,0,0,0,,It tastes awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.08,0:32:40.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Straight talker, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.84,0:32:45.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, hey!\NYou got tobacco?!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.18,0:32:50.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Knotweed leaves.\NWanna puff?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.89,0:32:53.47,Main,,0,0,0,,Heck nah,\NI ain't a caterpillar!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.60,0:32:56.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Tobacco's so scarce now.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.93,0:32:58.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.61,0:33:13.70,Main,,0,0,0,,The lady of the house keeps saying\Nshe wants to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.83,0:33:15.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Pay her a visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.79,0:33:17.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Is she very sick?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.33,0:33:23.17,Main,,0,0,0,,Morning sickness. Carrying a baby\Ncauses some women a lotta pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.88,0:33:28.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Like when you were born.\NYour momma had a tough time.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.56,0:33:37.89,Main,,0,0,0,,I came to visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.34,0:34:09.55,Main,,0,0,0,,M'lady...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.45,0:34:40.29,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. I shouldn't have\Nlet you get hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.33,0:34:44.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Forgive me, big sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.79,0:34:47.80,Main,,0,0,0,,M'lady, don't make\Nyourself worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.25,0:34:50.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Please get well soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.13,0:34:54.68,Main,,0,0,0,,<i>"Hikari Cigarettes"</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.99,0:35:16.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Your presence is requested!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.33,0:36:10.71,Main,,0,0,0,,A cigarette!\NYou wily old flimflam man!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.09,0:36:56.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Sonny, sonny!\NCome, come.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.72,0:36:58.84,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm busy now.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.22,0:37:02.22,Main,,0,0,0,,I got good news for ya.\NCome, come.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.06,0:37:07.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Sonny, wanna real bow and arrows?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.94,0:37:12.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Something perfect for ya.\NThe genuine article.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.48,0:37:17.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Steel arrowheads,\Nand a mighty fine bow and all.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.61,0:37:20.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Nobody'll know it's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.95,0:37:21.99,Main,,0,0,0,,For cigarettes?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.91,0:37:25.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Hikari.\NHow 'bout one box?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.29,0:37:27.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Gramps has them.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.58,0:37:31.33,Main,,0,0,0,,And there were only two inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.75,0:37:35.34,Main,,0,0,0,,You gave 'em to that wrinkly prune?!\NHey! Sonny!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.73,0:39:59.73,Main,,0,0,0,,<i>"To grown-up Mahito"</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.86,0:40:01.90,Main,,0,0,0,,<i>"From Mother\N1937, autumn"</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.74,0:40:10.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Mother's handwriting...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.62,0:40:18.25,Main,,0,0,0,,<i>"How Do You Live?"</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.96,0:40:22.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Mother left this for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.21,0:41:04.71,Main,,0,0,0,,- M'lady!\N- M'lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.01,0:41:07.80,Main,,0,0,0,,- M'lady!\N- M'lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.93,0:41:18.02,Main,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.85,0:41:21.86,Main,,0,0,0,,The lady of the house\Nain't in her room!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.07,0:41:25.15,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll go too!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.29,0:41:43.04,Main,,0,0,0,,She headed for the forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.21,0:41:44.54,Main,,0,0,0,,The lady did?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.84,0:41:47.51,Main,,0,0,0,,A while ago now.\NIt was bright out.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.55,0:41:50.59,Main,,0,0,0,,She must be in the forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.72,0:41:52.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Surely not!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.34,0:41:54.10,Main,,0,0,0,,No gray heron today.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.06,0:41:56.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Something's wrong!\NLet's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.60,0:42:05.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's not! She wouldn't have\Ngone that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.40,0:42:13.45,Main,,0,0,0,,I can't see a thing...\NHey, sonny!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.66,0:42:16.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Clog prints...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.70,0:42:20.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Sonny!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.47,0:42:31.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.43,0:42:33.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Pavestones.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.14,0:42:37.72,Main,,0,0,0,,C-Can't see 'em.\NI got night blindness.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.85,0:42:39.39,Main,,0,0,0,,It's an old path.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.52,0:42:41.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.27,0:42:44.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Ain't no way the lady\Nwould come here!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.77,0:42:47.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Maybe she didn't have a choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.43,0:43:16.59,Main,,0,0,0,,L-L-Lights!\NIt's a trap! A trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.10,0:43:21.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Heron man! Here I am!\NReturn Natsuko to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.31,0:43:26.48,Main,,0,0,0,,About time you came.\NNow, enter.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.48,0:43:30.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Go back, ma'am.\NI'll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.65,0:43:35.24,Main,,0,0,0,,You mustn't go! We maids can't hear\Nthe tower master's voice!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.74,0:43:38.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Only your bloodline can!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.78,0:43:42.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Then I must go!\NI have to bring Aunt Natsuko back!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.87,0:43:47.88,Main,,0,0,0,,No! You think you'd be better off\Nwithout her, don't ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.38,0:43:50.88,Main,,0,0,0,,So what's the point in going?!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.84,0:43:53.88,Main,,0,0,0,,He says my mother's alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.17,0:43:56.80,Main,,0,0,0,,I know it's a lie,\Nbut I have to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.35,0:44:02.47,Main,,0,0,0,,Wait! Ow ow ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.93,0:44:07.19,Main,,0,0,0,,My poor back!\NOw ow ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.21,0:44:35.51,Main,,0,0,0,,About time you came.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.18,0:44:43.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Step this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.56,0:44:47.56,Main,,0,0,0,,It's a trap! A trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.73,0:44:48.85,Main,,0,0,0,,I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.98,0:44:50.86,Main,,0,0,0,,If so, then why...?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:29.10,0:45:33.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Here she is.\NYour mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.78,0:45:43.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Why not get closer\Nand make sure for yourself...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:44.28,0:45:46.79,Main,,0,0,0,,It's a trap. A trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.87,0:45:51.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Wait, sonny...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.48,0:46:14.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.61,0:46:16.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.61,0:46:18.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.78,0:46:20.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Mo...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:43.38,0:46:47.18,Main,,0,0,0,,What a waste.\NOne of my better efforts.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:47.93,0:46:50.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Shouldn't have touched her.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:50.93,0:46:52.52,Main,,0,0,0,,How can you do this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.89,0:46:55.86,Main,,0,0,0,,If you'd like,\NI could remake her...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:56.23,0:46:58.65,Main,,0,0,0,,No! Don't dishonor my mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:59.15,0:47:02.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Angry? My heart is right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.24,0:47:04.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Best use your one arrow wisely.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:05.16,0:47:07.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Then it's my turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:07.53,0:47:11.58,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll bite your arrogant,\Nlying, swollen heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.70,0:47:13.75,Main,,0,0,0,,and rip it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:15.04,0:47:17.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Weakling, do your worst.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:18.13,0:47:19.00,Main,,0,0,0,,You fail!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:28.68,0:47:30.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Get away from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:31.64,0:47:33.77,Main,,0,0,0,,Drat! My molted feather!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.87,0:47:49.58,Main,,0,0,0,,This ain't good...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:50.66,0:47:53.08,Main,,0,0,0,,You got 'im!\NNice shooting!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:53.20,0:47:55.25,Main,,0,0,0,,The arrow flew by itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:11.72,0:48:14.73,Main,,0,0,0,,No! Not my #7 flight feather!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:18.27,0:48:20.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Dang it!\NThat wasn't fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:25.99,0:48:27.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't laugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:27.95,0:48:30.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Behold my fearsomeness...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:31.20,0:48:33.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Be gentle...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:47.18,0:48:48.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's not do that...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:49.14,0:48:50.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Where is Natsuko?!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:50.80,0:48:54.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Sonny, skewer that turkey!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:54.43,0:48:56.77,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey... Brilliantly done.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:58.06,0:49:01.98,Main,,0,0,0,,So tell me, how did you\Nfigure out my weakness?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:02.57,0:49:06.36,Main,,0,0,0,,You just told me.\NIt's your #7 flight feather.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:06.82,0:49:10.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Whoopsie daisy!\NLoose lips sink ships.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:11.16,0:49:13.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Take me to Natsuko.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:14.04,0:49:16.37,Main,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't go if I were you...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:33.68,0:49:38.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Foolish bird.\NI command you to be his guide.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:43.61,0:49:48.32,Main,,0,0,0,,No going back now.\NYou might end up regretting it.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:53.95,0:49:55.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Godspeed, soldier...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:58.71,0:50:00.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Not me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:03.58,0:50:05.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Not me!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:24.31,0:52:28.10,Main,,0,0,0,,"Those who seek my knowledge\Nshall die"...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:00.93,0:53:02.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:03.22,0:53:04.47,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's go eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:04.72,0:53:05.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:09.73,0:53:12.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's go!\NLet's go eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:12.73,0:53:13.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Get up!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:13.82,0:53:16.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Walk! Walk!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:20.95,0:53:22.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Someone opened the gate...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:54.40,0:53:56.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Get back, damn birds!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:34.61,0:54:35.65,Main,,0,0,0,,On your feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:37.78,0:54:38.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Move.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:41.53,0:54:44.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Move! The buried will wake.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:51.50,0:54:52.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Stand beside me.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:22.15,0:55:23.36,Main,,0,0,0,,It's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:24.70,0:55:27.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Walk backwards.\NDon't look back.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:37.67,0:55:39.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Why did you open the gate?!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:40.71,0:55:42.30,Main,,0,0,0,,The pelicans pushed me...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:42.47,0:55:43.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Show me that arrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:51.39,0:55:55.60,Main,,0,0,0,,The gray heron? No wonder\Nthe pelicans couldn't eat you.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:02.32,0:56:06.57,Main,,0,0,0,,The wind is up.\NThe tide'll be high. Follow me!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:30.18,0:56:31.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Push!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:50.32,0:56:52.62,Main,,0,0,0,,We've caught the wind!\NCome!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:03.25,0:57:04.42,Main,,0,0,0,,That scar...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:08.22,0:57:09.51,Main,,0,0,0,,My plaster came off.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:11.80,0:57:13.64,Main,,0,0,0,,I've got one too. Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:14.60,0:57:16.27,Main,,0,0,0,,A swamp thrasher got me.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:17.14,0:57:18.44,Main,,0,0,0,,"Swamp thrasher"?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:18.85,0:57:22.02,Main,,0,0,0,,A massive one.\NI ate it though.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:22.52,0:57:26.44,Main,,0,0,0,,A big wave's coming.\NAfter that, plain sailing.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:16.79,0:58:18.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Where'd you come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:20.04,0:58:21.17,Main,,0,0,0,,Up above...
Dialogue: 0,0:58:22.88,0:58:24.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Is it a nice place?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:26.50,0:58:27.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Not for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:30.22,0:58:33.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Have you seen a woman called Natsuko?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:34.47,0:58:36.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you sweet on her?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:38.97,0:58:43.27,Main,,0,0,0,,My father is...\NI'm trying to find her.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:44.73,0:58:46.82,Main,,0,0,0,,And what are you called?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:49.19,0:58:50.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Mahito.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:50.90,0:58:52.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Meaning "sincere one"...
Dialogue: 0,0:58:53.07,0:58:56.58,Main,,0,0,0,,So that's why you reek of death.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:57.58,0:58:58.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:02.67,0:59:04.33,Main,,0,0,0,,None are real.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:05.25,0:59:08.21,Main,,0,0,0,,In this world,\Nthe dead are the majority.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:13.93,0:59:15.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Stop rowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:47.25,0:59:48.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Who are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:48.92,0:59:51.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Buyers coming for our catch.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:51.96,0:59:53.51,Main,,0,0,0,,They saw that flag.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:56.22,1:00:00.60,Main,,0,0,0,,They're not able to kill.\NThat's my job.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:45.52,1:00:47.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Get off. Help me.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:47.69,1:00:49.23,Main,,0,0,0,,The warawara are coming.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:17.72,1:01:19.39,Main,,0,0,0,,No dilly-dallying!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:19.89,1:01:22.05,Main,,0,0,0,,That fish needs carving!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:34.90,1:01:36.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Lend a hand.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:59.72,1:02:00.80,Main,,0,0,0,,You try.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:06.10,1:02:07.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Right there.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:11.56,1:02:12.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Deeper!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:19.99,1:02:21.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Pull hard!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:31.12,1:02:33.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't spill the guts!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:33.88,1:02:36.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Warawara eat them so they can fly.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:32.52,1:03:33.89,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, get up and eat.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:35.10,1:03:37.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't touch those dolls.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:04.68,1:04:08.22,Main,,0,0,0,,They look like the grannies\Nat the residence.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:10.31,1:04:12.14,Main,,0,0,0,,They're protecting you.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:13.39,1:04:14.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Water's over there.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:39.71,1:04:40.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Kiriko.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:41.42,1:04:44.01,Main,,0,0,0,,How do you know my damn name?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:44.84,1:04:46.26,Main,,0,0,0,,It's Kiriko, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:46.84,1:04:52.31,Main,,0,0,0,,This world isn't like mine,\Nbut some things are similar.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:52.97,1:04:55.27,Main,,0,0,0,,I've always been here.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:55.89,1:05:00.27,Main,,0,0,0,,The Kiriko I know\Nis an old lady, like those dolls.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:01.15,1:05:02.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and eat.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:03.48,1:05:04.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Toilet?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:05.19,1:05:07.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Out there, in the yard.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:07.74,1:05:08.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:01.14,1:07:01.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Kiriko!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:04.40,1:07:06.02,Main,,0,0,0,,They mature, then fly.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:07.44,1:07:09.94,Main,,0,0,0,,They haven't flown for so long.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:21.25,1:07:22.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Little ones see them off.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:23.29,1:07:25.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Where are they going?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:25.42,1:07:27.42,Main,,0,0,0,,- To be born.\N- What?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:27.54,1:07:31.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Where you came from.\NTo be born up above.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:31.21,1:07:32.34,Main,,0,0,0,,As people?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:32.59,1:07:33.55,Main,,0,0,0,,What else?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:53.40,1:07:56.45,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm glad we could feed them well.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:12.46,1:08:15.51,Main,,0,0,0,,Pelicans! Dammit,\Nthey'll eat them all!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:30.15,1:08:31.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Lady Himi!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:47.21,1:08:48.33,Main,,0,0,0,,The warawara are burning!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:51.96,1:08:55.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Stop it!\NDon't burn the warawara!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:56.22,1:08:57.51,Main,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:04.56,1:09:07.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Damn birds'll stay away for now.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:07.52,1:09:10.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Without Lady Himi,\Nno more warawara.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:11.11,1:09:13.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Lady Himi! Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:25.75,1:09:28.67,Main,,0,0,0,,No more'll fly tonight.\NLet's eat.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:56.74,1:09:59.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Sorry grannies...
Dialogue: 0,1:10:43.20,1:10:46.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Young one,\Nput me out of my misery.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:46.91,1:10:49.79,Main,,0,0,0,,My wing is broken.\NI cannot fly.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:51.08,1:10:53.67,Main,,0,0,0,,You should've left the warawara alone!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:54.79,1:10:58.51,Main,,0,0,0,,My kind were brought to this hellscape
Dialogue: 0,1:10:58.63,1:11:02.30,Main,,0,0,0,,so we would eat the warawara.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:03.22,1:11:06.97,Main,,0,0,0,,This sea has few fish we can eat.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:08.56,1:11:11.43,Main,,0,0,0,,My kind were all starving.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:12.56,1:11:15.65,Main,,0,0,0,,<i>We flew as high as we could.</i>
Dialogue: 0,1:11:15.86,1:11:19.61,Main,,0,0,0,,<i>As high and far\Nas our wings could carry us.</i>
Dialogue: 0,1:11:20.11,1:11:24.20,Main,,0,0,0,,But... it always ended the same way.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:24.45,1:11:27.03,Main,,0,0,0,,We could only reach this island.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:31.16,1:11:35.17,Main,,0,0,0,,Now our newborns\Nare forgetting how to fly.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:35.92,1:11:38.84,Main,,0,0,0,,We eat the warawara...
Dialogue: 0,1:11:38.96,1:11:41.92,Main,,0,0,0,,The fire maiden burns us...
Dialogue: 0,1:11:45.68,1:11:50.47,Main,,0,0,0,,The sea here...\Nis cursed...
Dialogue: 0,1:11:57.86,1:12:02.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Rest in peace.\NIt was such a noble pelican...
Dialogue: 0,1:12:06.99,1:12:10.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah! You still have that?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:11.04,1:12:12.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:16.54,1:12:18.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Natsuko isn't here,\Nyou know.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:19.04,1:12:20.13,Main,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:21.00,1:12:23.21,Main,,0,0,0,,How about I take you to her?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:24.13,1:12:25.88,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll find her myself.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:27.72,1:12:30.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Wait. Hey, chief!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:36.23,1:12:38.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Arrogant little turd!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:48.11,1:12:49.45,Main,,0,0,0,,You'll bury it...?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:05.97,1:13:06.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:07.01,1:13:08.84,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm such a pushover.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:08.97,1:13:10.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:10.72,1:13:13.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Too far! Come back.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:14.27,1:13:15.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:18.10,1:13:19.73,Main,,0,0,0,,I can't stomach this.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:20.86,1:13:23.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't blame me if\NNatsuko gets eaten.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:24.11,1:13:26.82,Main,,0,0,0,,You said you'd eat my heart.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:32.58,1:13:33.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:33.87,1:13:35.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:37.96,1:13:40.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Spit it out.\NWhere is Natsuko?!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:42.29,1:13:43.25,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll rip this!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:43.75,1:13:46.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Try it!\NI'll tear you apart!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:48.17,1:13:51.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Ow ow ow!\NPlease stop!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:52.14,1:13:54.68,Main,,0,0,0,,You okay?\NI hardly ripped it.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:58.98,1:13:59.94,Main,,0,0,0,,It's ripped now.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:15.37,1:14:19.50,Main,,0,0,0,,This is crummy tea,\Nbut drink and make up.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:20.25,1:14:22.38,Main,,0,0,0,,We didn't fight.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:22.50,1:14:26.92,Main,,0,0,0,,He's a liar and a cheat,\Nbut I know he took Natsuko.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:27.05,1:14:30.43,Main,,0,0,0,,I hate to say it,\Nbut you overestimate me.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:30.55,1:14:32.97,Main,,0,0,0,,The wise cheat to survive.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:33.43,1:14:37.14,Main,,0,0,0,,A gray heron told me\Nall gray herons are liars.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:37.39,1:14:39.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Is that the truth,\Nor a lie?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:40.19,1:14:41.48,Main,,0,0,0,,- A lie!\N- The truth!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:42.27,1:14:46.40,Main,,0,0,0,,It's the truth.\NAll gray herons are liars.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:46.73,1:14:47.94,Main,,0,0,0,,That's a lie too!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:48.07,1:14:49.61,Main,,0,0,0,,This lie is true.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:53.49,1:14:57.83,Main,,0,0,0,,You're a fine pair.\NGo search for Natsuko together.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:58.66,1:15:00.87,Main,,0,0,0,,I have to tend to the warawara.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:01.04,1:15:03.88,Main,,0,0,0,,The tower master\Ntold you to guide him.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:04.50,1:15:07.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Stay vigilant,\Nand work together. Go.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:24.19,1:15:25.36,Main,,0,0,0,,It's Kiriko!
Dialogue: 0,1:15:25.73,1:15:27.90,Main,,0,0,0,,For good luck.\NTake it.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:28.86,1:15:30.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Will we meet again?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:30.24,1:15:31.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:31.69,1:15:32.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,1:15:33.20,1:15:34.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Do your best.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:44.75,1:15:46.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Miss Natsuko!
Dialogue: 0,1:15:47.59,1:15:49.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Miss Natsuko!
Dialogue: 0,1:15:53.38,1:15:56.09,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll get some men to stay here!
Dialogue: 0,1:15:56.22,1:16:01.10,Main,,0,0,0,,No, the factory mustn't stop.\NPlease return to your work.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:01.22,1:16:03.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Alright! We'll always be on call!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:03.94,1:16:05.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:16.53,1:16:20.83,Main,,0,0,0,,We've searched the pond,\Nthe hills, everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:21.20,1:16:23.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Natsuko, Mahito, and Kiriko.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:24.12,1:16:27.25,Main,,0,0,0,,A triple disappearance is unheard of.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:27.42,1:16:29.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Say, Mister Shoichi...
Dialogue: 0,1:16:30.17,1:16:34.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Every now and then,\Nstrange things happen here...
Dialogue: 0,1:16:34.67,1:16:39.47,Main,,0,0,0,,I've been working here\Nfor a good 60 years now,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:39.85,1:16:44.23,Main,,0,0,0,,and that tower out in the yard\Njust ain't right.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:45.69,1:16:49.11,Main,,0,0,0,,That thing sure weren't\Nbuilt by people.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:49.48,1:16:51.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh come on,\Nscary stories now?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:52.36,1:16:56.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Just before the Meiji Revolution,\Nit fell outta the sky!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:04.83,1:17:08.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Rumble rumble,\NBOOOOOM!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:10.17,1:17:12.88,Main,,0,0,0,,With an earth-rattling crash.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:13.42,1:17:14.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Like thunder?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:15.01,1:17:20.93,Main,,0,0,0,,There used to be a big pond,\Nbut the water all dried up.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:21.05,1:17:23.68,Main,,0,0,0,,That tower stands there now.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:38.03,1:17:42.83,Main,,0,0,0,,From what I heard,\NNatsuko's clever granduncle had it built.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:43.03,1:17:46.58,Main,,0,0,0,,No siree,\Nit came down from the sky!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:46.70,1:17:50.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Everybody was\Ntoo scared to go near it.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:50.71,1:17:55.76,Main,,0,0,0,,<i>After 30-odd years, the forest\Ngrew back, and the thing got buried.</i>
Dialogue: 0,1:17:56.63,1:18:00.39,Main,,0,0,0,,<i>Then, the granduncle discovered it.</i>
Dialogue: 0,1:18:00.89,1:18:03.64,Main,,0,0,0,,He became obsessed with it...
Dialogue: 0,1:18:03.76,1:18:08.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Because it was so rare,\Nhe built the tower around it.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:20.99,1:18:24.24,Main,,0,0,0,,So many people died or got hurt.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:24.37,1:18:28.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Plus, the granduncle\Nvanished into the tower...
Dialogue: 0,1:18:28.29,1:18:29.71,Main,,0,0,0,,He sure did.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:30.46,1:18:36.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Mahito's mother Hisako\Nalso went missing once.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:37.59,1:18:40.68,Main,,0,0,0,,<i>We searched the whole village.</i>
Dialogue: 0,1:18:41.13,1:18:45.30,Main,,0,0,0,,<i>Then after a year,\Nshe came back, fit as a fiddle.</i>
Dialogue: 0,1:18:45.76,1:18:48.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Looking the same as she was before.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:48.77,1:18:53.06,Main,,0,0,0,,No memory of it,\Nand grinning, but...
Dialogue: 0,1:18:54.27,1:18:55.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Bizarre, ain't it?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:57.82,1:18:59.32,Main,,0,0,0,,We have the tower key?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:59.78,1:19:01.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Yessir, I think...
Dialogue: 0,1:19:01.61,1:19:02.91,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll go there now.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:21.17,1:19:22.55,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm pooped...
Dialogue: 0,1:19:24.26,1:19:27.35,Main,,0,0,0,,These legs weren't made for walking.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:28.47,1:19:32.44,Main,,0,0,0,,I won't be able to make it\Nto where Natsuko is.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:32.73,1:19:36.40,Main,,0,0,0,,If only I could block this hole,\NI could fly...
Dialogue: 0,1:19:37.11,1:19:38.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Shove a stick in it or something.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:39.73,1:19:44.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Easy to say. The hole maker\Nhas to fill it, or it won't work!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:45.49,1:19:47.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Is that lie true?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:47.74,1:19:49.99,Main,,0,0,0,,I never tell lies!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:55.17,1:19:57.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Be gentle...
Dialogue: 0,1:20:06.59,1:20:09.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Make that part smoother...
Dialogue: 0,1:20:09.18,1:20:10.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:13.10,1:20:17.10,Main,,0,0,0,,It's through! Gently,\Nor you'll break your beak.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:19.57,1:20:20.61,Main,,0,0,0,,How's that?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:29.28,1:20:33.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Look at me,\Ngorgeous and powerful!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:34.71,1:20:36.17,Main,,0,0,0,,Can you fly?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:38.50,1:20:42.26,Main,,0,0,0,,I ain't your friend or your ally, kid.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:43.76,1:20:49.01,Main,,0,0,0,,So long. You'll have to find Natsuko,\Nand get out of here,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:49.14,1:20:51.81,Main,,0,0,0,,all on your lonesome...
Dialogue: 0,1:20:59.40,1:21:00.61,Main,,0,0,0,,It came out?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:00.94,1:21:02.65,Main,,0,0,0,,No, it just...
Dialogue: 0,1:21:03.82,1:21:06.28,Main,,0,0,0,,It sticks out a wee bit, so...
Dialogue: 0,1:21:06.70,1:21:09.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Here! This part bugs me!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:09.87,1:21:12.95,Main,,0,0,0,,There! There!\NOh, don't take too much off...
Dialogue: 0,1:21:13.08,1:21:14.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:19.25,1:21:20.42,Main,,0,0,0,,It's a home.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:20.54,1:21:23.88,Main,,0,0,0,,The blacksmith's.\NShh! Duck down!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:28.55,1:21:29.93,Main,,0,0,0,,That's a big parakeet.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:30.09,1:21:33.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Weird... Why are they\Nhanging around?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:34.02,1:21:35.77,Main,,0,0,0,,They ate the blacksmith?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:35.98,1:21:37.35,Main,,0,0,0,,They eat people?!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:37.48,1:21:39.19,Main,,0,0,0,,Elephants too.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:40.27,1:21:44.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Like the pelicans, the master\Nbrought them, and they bred.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:46.40,1:21:51.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Gotta pass through there,\Nor you can't get to Natsuko.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:51.95,1:21:55.08,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll draw 'em out,\Nthen you dash in.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:55.20,1:21:56.29,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll try.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:58.77,1:23:00.56,Main,,0,0,0,,We have been waiting.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:01.94,1:23:05.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Is there a Natsuko here?\NI'm looking for her.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:06.94,1:23:08.61,Main,,0,0,0,,This way, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:30.63,1:23:31.63,Main,,0,0,0,,This way.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:32.55,1:23:35.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Damn you!\NIs this how you ate Natsuko?!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:36.22,1:23:38.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Natsuko has baby.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:38.43,1:23:39.81,Main,,0,0,0,,We not eat baby.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:40.31,1:23:42.06,Main,,0,0,0,,You not have baby.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:42.23,1:23:43.77,Main,,0,0,0,,Eatable! Eatable!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:46.52,1:23:47.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Himi! It's Himi!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:05.00,1:24:08.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Stupid. Those parakeets\Nnearly stewed you.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:09.42,1:24:13.17,Main,,0,0,0,,You're Himi?\NThank you for saving my life.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:14.09,1:24:17.09,Main,,0,0,0,,You're that brat\Nwho was with Kiriko.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:17.89,1:24:21.72,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm Mahito. I'm looking\Nfor someone called Natsuko.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:22.27,1:24:24.19,Main,,0,0,0,,Natsuko...\NMy little sister?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:25.06,1:24:26.10,Main,,0,0,0,,"Little sister"?!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:29.27,1:24:30.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Come.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:31.48,1:24:32.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Time's wasting.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:07.56,1:25:08.90,Main,,0,0,0,,This is my home.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:42.72,1:25:44.81,Main,,0,0,0,,It's like a tower I know.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:45.02,1:25:47.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Sure, it's the same one.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:47.35,1:25:50.86,Main,,0,0,0,,It stands straddling\Nall kinds of worlds.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:51.15,1:25:52.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Come in.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:21.72,1:26:22.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Eat it.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:23.68,1:26:25.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Hurry, the jam'll drip.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:33.73,1:26:36.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Kiriko loves my bread too.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:39.70,1:26:40.99,Main,,0,0,0,,It's delicious!
Dialogue: 0,1:26:41.53,1:26:44.78,Main,,0,0,0,,It's like the bread\Nmy mother used to bake!
Dialogue: 0,1:26:45.78,1:26:47.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Natsuko is your mother?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:48.29,1:26:49.37,Main,,0,0,0,,She's not.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:49.96,1:26:53.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Natsuko is someone...\Nmy father likes.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:54.13,1:26:55.92,Main,,0,0,0,,My mother died.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:56.42,1:26:57.71,Main,,0,0,0,,As did mine.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:59.34,1:27:02.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Eat lots. We'll be going\Ndeep inside.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:08.97,1:27:12.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Careful. You get lost,\Nyou never get out.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:21.07,1:27:22.24,Main,,0,0,0,,It's guarded...
Dialogue: 0,1:27:44.05,1:27:48.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Careful. In here,\Nmy power has limits.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:50.35,1:27:51.43,Main,,0,0,0,,This way.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:01.11,1:28:02.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Doors to where?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:02.32,1:28:04.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Quiet. You'll mess me up.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:10.66,1:28:11.62,Main,,0,0,0,,This one.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:14.33,1:28:15.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't get sucked in.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:20.67,1:28:21.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Father?!
Dialogue: 0,1:28:22.09,1:28:23.67,Main,,0,0,0,,That's your father?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:24.43,1:28:27.18,Main,,0,0,0,,If you want to go home,\Nopen this.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:27.34,1:28:30.18,Main,,0,0,0,,But Natsuko...\NI can't leave alone!
Dialogue: 0,1:28:30.31,1:28:33.93,Main,,0,0,0,,She doesn't want to leave.\NShe'll have her baby.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:36.98,1:28:38.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Parakeets!
Dialogue: 0,1:28:44.03,1:28:47.03,Main,,0,0,0,,We're trapped.\NIn here! Turn it hard!
Dialogue: 0,1:28:47.45,1:28:49.87,Main,,0,0,0,,You mustn't let go.\NReady?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:51.37,1:28:54.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Grab the other knob!\NShut the door!
Dialogue: 0,1:29:00.21,1:29:02.13,Main,,0,0,0,,- Where are we?\N- Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,1:29:03.55,1:29:06.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Once you let go,\Nit's lost forever.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:18.27,1:29:19.48,Main,,0,0,0,,It's Mahito!
Dialogue: 0,1:29:21.11,1:29:22.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Mahito!
Dialogue: 0,1:29:23.78,1:29:25.74,Main,,0,0,0,,- Father!\N- Want to stay?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:26.07,1:29:27.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Just let go.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:27.53,1:29:29.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Not without Natsuko!
Dialogue: 0,1:29:36.83,1:29:38.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Taste my blade, monsters!
Dialogue: 0,1:29:52.97,1:29:55.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Mahito turned into a parakeet...
Dialogue: 0,1:29:55.77,1:29:57.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Father, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:58.48,1:30:00.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Mister Shoichi...
Dialogue: 0,1:30:00.27,1:30:03.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Mahito's a budgie now!
Dialogue: 0,1:30:39.18,1:30:40.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't touch the stone.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:41.06,1:30:43.48,Main,,0,0,0,,It's not happy we're here.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:52.74,1:30:55.53,Main,,0,0,0,,The delivery room.\NNatsuko's there.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:59.75,1:31:03.42,Main,,0,0,0,,The stone's aware of us,\Nand upset. I wouldn't go in.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:05.04,1:31:06.21,Main,,0,0,0,,I have to go.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:07.59,1:31:08.67,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll wait here.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:58.81,1:32:01.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Natsuko, it's Mahito.\NNatsuko?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:20.37,1:32:24.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Natsuko, it's Mahito!\NI've come for you!
Dialogue: 0,1:32:24.75,1:32:27.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Natsuko! Let's go home!
Dialogue: 0,1:32:30.88,1:32:33.67,Main,,0,0,0,,You... What are you doing here?!
Dialogue: 0,1:32:34.80,1:32:37.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Go back! Now!
Dialogue: 0,1:32:41.14,1:32:42.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's go together!
Dialogue: 0,1:32:43.68,1:32:46.31,Main,,0,0,0,,I absolutely hate you!\NGet out!
Dialogue: 0,1:32:49.94,1:32:52.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Go back! Now!
Dialogue: 0,1:33:01.83,1:33:04.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Natsuko...\NMother!
Dialogue: 0,1:33:08.58,1:33:09.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Mother!
Dialogue: 0,1:33:13.30,1:33:15.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Mother! Let's go home!
Dialogue: 0,1:33:24.77,1:33:26.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Mahito, run!
Dialogue: 0,1:33:29.65,1:33:31.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Natsuko! Mother!
Dialogue: 0,1:34:17.53,1:34:21.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Master of the great stone,\Nhear my plea.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:22.57,1:34:26.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Let my sister lying there...\Ngo home...
Dialogue: 0,1:34:26.45,1:34:29.37,Main,,0,0,0,,...with this boy\Nwho will be her son.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:32.83,1:34:37.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Natsuko. Natsuko.\NCome to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:37.63,1:34:39.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Up you get.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:44.89,1:34:48.35,Main,,0,0,0,,That's it. Good girl.\NCome to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:34.25,1:36:37.63,Main,,0,0,0,,You have come,\Nmy descendant.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:41.59,1:36:43.01,Main,,0,0,0,,My name is Mahito.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:43.67,1:36:46.68,Main,,0,0,0,,You're the tower master?\NMy great-granduncle?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:47.47,1:36:50.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Wait there. Quietly.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:19.42,1:37:21.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Now this world...
Dialogue: 0,1:37:23.05,1:37:25.30,Main,,0,0,0,,...will last another day.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:26.76,1:37:30.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Another day?!\NIt only lasts that long?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:31.18,1:37:32.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Come.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:29.11,1:38:30.57,Main,,0,0,0,,My world,
Dialogue: 0,1:38:31.20,1:38:35.99,Main,,0,0,0,,my power, everything,\Ncomes from this stone.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:36.79,1:38:39.91,Main,,0,0,0,,That stone created this sea world?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:40.92,1:38:43.00,Main,,0,0,0,,There is more to be done.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:43.63,1:38:47.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Worlds are living things.\NMold and bugs infest them.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:48.51,1:38:50.68,Main,,0,0,0,,And I have grown old.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:50.88,1:38:53.64,Main,,0,0,0,,I seek a successor.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:56.22,1:39:00.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Mahito, will you continue my work?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:00.94,1:39:02.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Me...?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:02.52,1:39:07.53,Main,,0,0,0,,My successor must come\Nfrom my bloodline.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:07.65,1:39:10.15,Main,,0,0,0,,That is my contract with the stone.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:10.95,1:39:13.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Whether this world becomes beautiful,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:14.16,1:39:18.04,Main,,0,0,0,,or an abomination,\Nis entirely in your hands.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:18.70,1:39:20.46,Main,,0,0,0,,You mean your blocks?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:22.17,1:39:25.50,Main,,0,0,0,,You may add one of these blocks to it.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:31.63,1:39:36.01,Main,,0,0,0,,You can make this world\Na more harmonious place.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:39.97,1:39:41.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Those aren't wooden.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:42.14,1:39:45.11,Main,,0,0,0,,It's stone for making tombs.\NIt's malicious.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:49.40,1:39:50.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Correct.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:50.82,1:39:53.74,Main,,0,0,0,,That knowledge is why I choose you.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:45.25,1:40:46.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,1:40:46.58,1:40:47.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Save the chit-chat!
Dialogue: 0,1:41:09.48,1:41:10.77,Main,,0,0,0,,Himi's been caught.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:11.07,1:41:12.23,Main,,0,0,0,,She'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:12.36,1:41:13.49,Main,,0,0,0,,We must save her!
Dialogue: 0,1:42:09.50,1:42:10.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Is Himi alright?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:10.96,1:42:13.38,Main,,0,0,0,,They'll take her to their lord.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:13.50,1:42:14.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Their lord?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:14.67,1:42:16.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Your great-granduncle.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:17.63,1:42:21.01,Main,,0,0,0,,They'll use her\Nto make a deal with him.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:21.14,1:42:22.30,Main,,0,0,0,,A deal?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:22.76,1:42:24.93,Main,,0,0,0,,So they get everything.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:25.22,1:42:28.02,Main,,0,0,0,,The tower's full of parakeets now.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:28.94,1:42:31.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Your transgression\Ngave them an excuse.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:32.15,1:42:33.40,Main,,0,0,0,,"Transgression"?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:33.52,1:42:37.11,Main,,0,0,0,,The taboo.\NYou entered the delivery room.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:37.24,1:42:38.36,Main,,0,0,0,,A no-no.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:40.86,1:42:42.82,Main,,0,0,0,,But Himi didn't enter.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:42.95,1:42:44.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Taking you was taboo too.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:46.24,1:42:47.79,Main,,0,0,0,,This is a lookout.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:52.54,1:42:53.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Higher!
Dialogue: 0,1:43:00.88,1:43:04.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Subjects, this is far enough!\NAwait good news!
Dialogue: 0,1:43:05.51,1:43:07.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Let us accompany you!
Dialogue: 0,1:43:07.72,1:43:09.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Please let us!
Dialogue: 0,1:43:10.81,1:43:15.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Your sincerity is appreciated!\NHowever, this is my duty.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:16.23,1:43:18.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Subjects, live well!
Dialogue: 0,1:43:21.11,1:43:23.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Three cheers for our parakeet king!
Dialogue: 0,1:45:12.02,1:45:13.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Be still!
Dialogue: 0,1:45:13.68,1:45:17.65,Main,,0,0,0,,We carry Lady Himi,\Nour lord's descendant!
Dialogue: 0,1:45:18.27,1:45:19.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Yield to us!
Dialogue: 0,1:45:29.07,1:45:30.45,Main,,0,0,0,,H-Heaven!
Dialogue: 0,1:45:30.58,1:45:31.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Our ancestors!
Dialogue: 0,1:45:35.12,1:45:36.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Paradise!
Dialogue: 0,1:45:36.33,1:45:38.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Your Majesty,\Nis this paradise?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:39.79,1:45:41.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Be silent.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:41.42,1:45:42.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Look at that!
Dialogue: 0,1:45:42.92,1:45:44.34,Main,,0,0,0,,So pretty...
Dialogue: 0,1:46:02.44,1:46:05.40,Main,,0,0,0,,So, you made it.\NHave a seat.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:06.19,1:46:08.03,Main,,0,0,0,,No, we shall walk.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:29.26,1:46:32.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Entering the delivery room was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:32.55,1:46:36.64,Main,,0,0,0,,It is no laughing matter.\NA grave transgression.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:37.81,1:46:42.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Unquestionably. The stone\Nis shimmering dangerously.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:42.77,1:46:45.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Nevertheless,\Nyoung souls are precious.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:46.78,1:46:50.66,Main,,0,0,0,,As king, I cannot\Ndisregard a transgressor.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:51.49,1:46:56.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Give me time. I want Mahito\Nto become my successor.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:22.31,1:47:23.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Granduncle...
Dialogue: 0,1:47:26.02,1:47:29.32,Main,,0,0,0,,We must protect our world,\Nor it shall perish.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:29.90,1:47:34.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Mahito is a good boy.\NIt seems I must let him go.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:39.00,1:47:40.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Granduncle!
Dialogue: 0,1:47:43.46,1:47:45.04,Main,,0,0,0,,You must go too.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:07.98,1:48:09.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Th-That's it!
Dialogue: 0,1:48:09.73,1:48:10.99,Main,,0,0,0,,That passage.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:25.88,1:48:27.67,Main,,0,0,0,,I've been here before.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:27.79,1:48:28.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Yow! Youch!
Dialogue: 0,1:48:33.76,1:48:37.14,Main,,0,0,0,,I've never been this far in before...
Dialogue: 0,1:48:47.73,1:48:49.82,Main,,0,0,0,,We should return, Majesty!
Dialogue: 0,1:48:49.94,1:48:53.61,Main,,0,0,0,,I shall go. Make sure you\Nmake it back alive,
Dialogue: 0,1:48:54.24,1:48:56.61,Main,,0,0,0,,and tell them I was a true king.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:56.74,1:48:58.53,Main,,0,0,0,,- We will!\N- Fare thee well!
Dialogue: 0,1:49:37.36,1:49:41.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey chief, ain't it time\Nwe got outta here?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:41.41,1:49:43.54,Main,,0,0,0,,This way. Himi's calling.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:44.08,1:49:46.58,Main,,0,0,0,,I can't hear diddly-squat...
Dialogue: 0,1:49:48.92,1:49:50.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Himi!
Dialogue: 0,1:49:54.80,1:49:55.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Mahito!
Dialogue: 0,1:49:59.43,1:50:02.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Himi! Are you alright?!\NDid they hurt you?!
Dialogue: 0,1:50:02.81,1:50:03.85,Main,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,1:50:04.72,1:50:07.98,Main,,0,0,0,,I thought I'd lost you.\NI'm so glad!
Dialogue: 0,1:50:14.11,1:50:16.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Granduncle's waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:16.36,1:50:18.36,Main,,0,0,0,,I know. I'll go to him.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:18.57,1:50:20.91,Main,,0,0,0,,This feels wrong. Don't...
Dialogue: 0,1:50:21.03,1:50:22.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:26.45,1:50:27.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:33.00,1:50:34.71,Main,,0,0,0,,It's getting dark!
Dialogue: 0,1:51:07.54,1:51:08.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Stone blocks...
Dialogue: 0,1:51:10.92,1:51:14.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Better not touch them.\NThey're still powerful...
Dialogue: 0,1:51:39.99,1:51:42.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Granduncle,\NI've brought Mahito.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:43.41,1:51:44.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Here I am.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:48.24,1:51:52.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Look. These stones\Nare not stained with malice.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:02.30,1:52:07.05,Main,,0,0,0,,I traveled the far reaches of\Ntime and space to find them.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:09.18,1:52:14.44,Main,,0,0,0,,There are 13 in all.\NStack them once every three days.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:15.23,1:52:20.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Build your own tower.\NA kingdom freed from malice.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:22.45,1:52:26.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Create a world of bounty,\Npeace, and beauty.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:39.63,1:52:41.63,Main,,0,0,0,,I made this scar myself.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:42.80,1:52:44.93,Main,,0,0,0,,It's a sign of my malice.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:47.43,1:52:49.43,Main,,0,0,0,,I can't touch those stones.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:50.10,1:52:52.85,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll go back with Natsuko,\Nmy mother.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:53.85,1:52:58.94,Main,,0,0,0,,You'll return to a foolish world\Nof rampant murder and thievery?
Dialogue: 0,1:52:59.77,1:53:02.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Soon it shall be consumed by flames.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:03.07,1:53:07.32,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll make friends. Like Himi,\NKiriko, and the heron man.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:08.32,1:53:09.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,1:53:09.70,1:53:15.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Make friends. Return to your world.\NBut first, stack the stones.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:15.96,1:53:17.42,Main,,0,0,0,,There is no time!
Dialogue: 0,1:53:18.04,1:53:20.42,Main,,0,0,0,,<i>I cannot keep my tower standing.</i>
Dialogue: 0,1:53:31.10,1:53:36.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Traitor! You would place the fate\Nof the empire upon mere stones?!
Dialogue: 0,1:53:44.15,1:53:45.95,Main,,0,0,0,,B-Be still. Still.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:47.07,1:53:48.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,1:54:00.29,1:54:04.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Himi! Mahito!\NReturn to the corridor of time!
Dialogue: 0,1:54:04.13,1:54:05.59,Main,,0,0,0,,To your own time!
Dialogue: 0,1:54:06.38,1:54:07.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Granduncle!
Dialogue: 0,1:54:18.98,1:54:22.11,Main,,0,0,0,,The planet's splitting!\NGrab on!
Dialogue: 0,1:54:24.78,1:54:26.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Too much...
Dialogue: 0,1:54:42.75,1:54:45.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Granduncle! Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,1:54:46.55,1:54:47.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,1:54:50.22,1:54:51.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Hurry, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,1:55:17.62,1:55:18.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Miss Natsuko!
Dialogue: 0,1:55:30.88,1:55:32.80,Main,,0,0,0,,This is it!\NMahito, you go in.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:32.97,1:55:34.18,Main,,0,0,0,,What about you?!
Dialogue: 0,1:55:35.01,1:55:38.47,Main,,0,0,0,,Mine's another.\NI'm going to be your mother.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:39.02,1:55:41.31,Main,,0,0,0,,But you'll die in the hospital fire!
Dialogue: 0,1:55:41.81,1:55:45.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Fire doesn't scare me.\NI'll be so lucky to have you.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:45.61,1:55:48.15,Main,,0,0,0,,No! Himi, you've got to live!
Dialogue: 0,1:55:48.36,1:55:50.36,Main,,0,0,0,,You're a good boy!
Dialogue: 0,1:55:56.62,1:55:57.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Holy moly!
Dialogue: 0,1:56:00.29,1:56:02.16,Main,,0,0,0,,- Mother!\N- Mahito!
Dialogue: 0,1:56:02.29,1:56:03.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness!
Dialogue: 0,1:56:03.50,1:56:06.50,Main,,0,0,0,,- Sister!\N- All the best for the birth.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:06.67,1:56:07.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Now, hurry.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:36.74,1:56:38.33,Main,,0,0,0,,How adorable!
Dialogue: 0,1:57:02.68,1:57:05.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey! This way!
Dialogue: 0,1:57:13.86,1:57:17.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Good. The pelicans made it out too.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:17.57,1:57:19.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, Mahito.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:20.24,1:57:22.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Do you remember where we were?
Dialogue: 0,1:57:23.25,1:57:24.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Of course I do.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:24.58,1:57:26.42,Main,,0,0,0,,That's bad. Forget.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:26.54,1:57:27.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,1:57:27.67,1:57:29.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Forgetting is normal.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:31.25,1:57:33.13,Main,,0,0,0,,No keepsakes, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:57:40.93,1:57:45.73,Main,,0,0,0,,That's a powerful charm.\NWay too powerful for me...
Dialogue: 0,1:57:46.56,1:57:48.81,Main,,0,0,0,,That's one of them stones.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:49.15,1:57:51.61,Main,,0,0,0,,From that field full of them.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:51.90,1:57:54.19,Main,,0,0,0,,Can't trust amateurs like you.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:54.94,1:57:57.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, that stone ain't powerful.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:57.86,1:58:00.24,Main,,0,0,0,,You'll forget in time.\NYou should.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:05.54,1:58:07.62,Main,,0,0,0,,So long, friend.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:20.05,1:58:22.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Ow ow ow! Yeesh...
Dialogue: 0,1:58:22.14,1:58:23.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Kiriko!
Dialogue: 0,1:58:24.72,1:58:25.68,Main,,0,0,0,,The king?!
Dialogue: 0,1:58:36.07,1:58:38.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Natsuko! Mahito!
Dialogue: 0,1:58:38.49,1:58:40.11,Main,,0,0,0,,- Shoichi!\N- Father!
Dialogue: 0,1:58:47.54,1:58:49.37,Main,,0,0,0,,<i>Two years after the war,</i>
Dialogue: 0,1:58:51.50,1:58:52.96,Main,,0,0,0,,<i>we returned to Tokyo.</i>
Dialogue: 0,1:58:55.75,1:58:57.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey! Mahito!
Dialogue: 0,1:58:59.17,1:59:00.34,Main,,0,0,0,,We're going!
Dialogue: 0,1:59:01.43,1:59:02.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Coming!
Dialogue: 0,1:59:38.17,1:59:43.84,Main,,0,0,0,,<i>The clear sky on the day I was born</i>
Dialogue: 0,1:59:45.47,1:59:51.44,Main,,0,0,0,,<i>was so high, distant, and endless</i>
Dialogue: 0,1:59:53.52,1:59:59.32,Main,,0,0,0,,<i>The day I heard a voice\Npatting me on the back</i>
Dialogue: 0,2:00:00.94,2:00:05.28,Main,,0,0,0,,<i>telling me to go ahead</i>
Dialogue: 0,2:00:07.41,2:00:13.08,Main,,0,0,0,,<i>Faces I met in the seasons,</i>
Dialogue: 0,2:00:14.71,2:00:20.71,Main,,0,0,0,,<i>at times hurting one another</i>
Dialogue: 0,2:00:22.76,2:00:28.56,Main,,0,0,0,,<i>Shine by the light, the shadow extends</i>
Dialogue: 0,2:00:29.89,2:00:34.52,Main,,0,0,0,,<i>as the sky grows further away</i>
Dialogue: 0,2:00:39.32,2:00:45.32,Main,,0,0,0,,<i>I catch the wind and start running,\Novercoming the rubble</i>
Dialogue: 0,2:00:45.45,2:00:51.45,Main,,0,0,0,,<i>At the end of this road,\Nsomeone is waiting for me</i>
Dialogue: 0,2:00:51.62,2:00:58.63,Main,,0,0,0,,<i>Dream of light shining through,\Nat any day of the week</i>
Dialogue: 0,2:01:00.88,2:01:06.93,Main,,0,0,0,,<i>Open the door this moment,\Nlike revealing hidden secrets</i>
Dialogue: 0,2:01:07.05,2:01:13.43,Main,,0,0,0,,<i>Can't hold myself longing for more,\Nlike the spinning globe</i>
Dialogue: 0,2:01:25.86,2:01:31.37,Main,,0,0,0,,<i>The person I loved</i>
Dialogue: 0,2:01:33.16,2:01:39.17,Main,,0,0,0,,<i>has gone to somewhere no one knows</i>
Dialogue: 0,2:01:41.29,2:01:46.97,Main,,0,0,0,,<i>With the usual kind\Nsmile as any other day,</i>
Dialogue: 0,2:01:48.55,2:01:52.89,Main,,0,0,0,,<i>still somewhere far away</i>
Dialogue: 0,2:01:57.69,2:02:03.86,Main,,0,0,0,,<i>I take in the rain and start singing,\Nnot minding if seen</i>
Dialogue: 0,2:02:03.98,2:02:09.95,Main,,0,0,0,,<i>This road continues\Nbecause I wished it would continue</i>
Dialogue: 0,2:02:10.07,2:02:17.08,Main,,0,0,0,,<i>I dream of meeting again,\Nfor ever and ever</i>
Dialogue: 0,2:02:19.29,2:02:25.21,Main,,0,0,0,,<i>I grasped the fragment firmly,\Nso the secret remains</i>
Dialogue: 0,2:02:25.38,2:02:31.80,Main,,0,0,0,,<i>I'll keep longing till the end,\Nlike the spinning globe</i>
Dialogue: 0,2:02:38.02,2:02:44.78,Main,,0,0,0,,<i>It all starts from an innocent wish\Nmade long ago</i>
Dialogue: 0,2:02:45.86,2:02:52.87,Main,,0,0,0,,<i>Carrying the loneliness in my heart,\NI turn the corner</i>
Dialogue: 0,2:02:56.95,2:03:03.04,Main,,0,0,0,,<i>I catch the wind and start running,\Novercoming the rubble</i>
Dialogue: 0,2:03:03.17,2:03:09.17,Main,,0,0,0,,<i>At the end of this road,\Nsomeone is waiting for me</i>
Dialogue: 0,2:03:09.30,2:03:16.31,Main,,0,0,0,,<i>Dream of light shining through,\Nat any day of the week</i>
Dialogue: 0,2:03:18.52,2:03:24.61,Main,,0,0,0,,<i>Open the door this moment,\Nlike revealing hidden secrets</i>
Dialogue: 0,2:03:24.73,2:03:30.78,Main,,0,0,0,,<i>The joy of holding ones hand,\Nthe suffering of losing one</i>
Dialogue: 0,2:03:30.90,2:03:37.20,Main,,0,0,0,,<i>Can't hold myself from picturing,\Nlike the spinning globe</i>
